# Task 1: Read a File and Handle Errors

- This program opens and reads a text file named sample.txt using with keyword and error handling using try exception block
- It then prints the content line by line using the readline function by using a loop
- Error handling done to ensure proper flow of code

# Task 2: Write and Append Data to a File

- This program takes user input to write the data into a file and another input to append data into the same file
- Finally reads and display the content into the terminal